    description: "Pipe weld positioner PP3\u00a0is specially designed and manufactured for the purpose of meeting the requirements of enhancing productivity, increasing the extent of ",
    body: "<p>Pipe weld positioner PP3 is specially designed and manufactured for the purpose of meeting the requirements of enhancing productivity, increasing the extent of automatic, reducing welder’s working intensity and adapting to piping workshop prefabrication. The welding head will be relatively fixed, while the piping spool piece revolving at a specific rate, and the high efficient and low cost shielded welding or SAW process is adopted, so it has the features of easy-operation, reliable-performance and wide-application field.</p>\n<p>1. Pipe weld positioner PP3 welding machine including: manipulator, welding rotator, and electric system etc, mainly used to weld the butt welding seam which formed from the pipe 、pipe elbow 、pipe flange 、perpendicular tee pipe . The welding head will be relatively fixed, while the piping spool piece revolving at a specific rate, and the high efficient and low cost shielded welding or SAW process is adopted, so it has the features of easy-operation, reliable-performance and wide-application field，and which enhancing productivity, increasing the extent of automatic, reducing welder’s working intensity and adapting to piping workshop prefabrication.</p>\n<p>Parameter:</p>\n<p>Pipe weld positioner main parameter:</p>\n<p>Load capacity: 3ton</p>\n<p>Applied work piece dia./mm:Φ100～Φ935</p>\n<p>Rotation speed/mm/min100～1000</p>\n<p>Structure characteristics</p>\n<p>p ipe positioner PP3 welding manipulator consists of column ,lifting slide unit, rotation roller , the column fixed on the bottom bracket , through turn round organization can turn ± 90 °by manual , at the front of lifting slide along fixed a set of assistance compress tightly organization, easy to compress tightly the work piece in weld the process, lend support to the pressure is 450 kgf, on the side column has a horizontal beam for reserving to install welding control organization.</p>\n<p>Turn roller is divided into powered part and idle part, powered part with column fixed on the bottom bracket, the reducer is a kind of special model which adopt to apply to pipe prefabrication product, can adapt the pipe diameter reach Ø50-600 mm, its motor power is 0.75 kw, electric voltage is three phase 240V, 60 Hz; The idle part doesn't equip motor, mainly prop up the work piece, Another the speed is adjust by AC INVERTER to realize step-less speed adjustment with digital display that the customer can preset parameters;</p>\n<p>The electricity of this set equipments control the system orientation communicate three phase 380V, 50 Hz of power supply request, Roller top end leaves ground to be apart from for the 650 mm, the customer can increment or decrease mat piece according to the size of the work piece during welding.</p>\n<p>Performance：</p>\n<p>Pipe weld positioner can do welding, cutting and grinding through clamping rotating and tilting thee pipes. If needed, we can supply 2— dimensional adjustable torch clamping system, by this way, automatically operation can come true.。</p>\n<p>Pipe weld positioner has essential advantages as it can be used for pipes with elbows,tee pieces or other offset loads.</p>\n<p>if there is any need, we can supply specical clamps or clamping rollers to clamp workpiece which has small clamping space.</p>\n<p>Pipe weld positioner is used in petrochemical machinery, engineering machinery , wind power equipment, construction &amp; bridge, shipbuilding, food &amp; pharmaceutical and other industries</p>\n<p>Welding Postioner for all kind welding girth seam and Long seam</p>\n<p>Welding Positioner with 1-Axis for Robot cobot Welding</p>\n\n<div class=\"article-images\">\n<img src=\"/images/wp/PR-1.png\" alt=\"Pipe weld positioner\" />\n<img src=\"/images/wr/wr00-21.jpg\" alt=\"Pipe weld positioner\" />\n<img src=\"/images/wr/wr00-40.jpg\" alt=\"Pipe weld positioner\" />\n<img src=\"/images/wp/wp-03.jpg\" alt=\"welding girth seam\" />\n</div>",
