    description: "POWER PACK Features &amp; Details",
    body: "<p>truck tailgate lift, scissor lift POWER PACK</p>\n<p>POWER PACK Features &amp; Details</p>\n<p>【HYDRULIC PUMP DOUBLE ACTING 】- This electric hydraulic pump is the perfect replacement pump for 12V DC remotely controlled hydraulic systems. Adopted durable materials, the hydraulic pump can resist corrosion and weariness, with high strength and hardness, to ensure its longer lifespans.</p>\n<p>【POWER UNIT SPECIFICATIONS】- The pump power unit kit features double-acting actions, 6/10/12-quart metal cylinder reservoir; standard duty 12V DC motor; SAE # 6 Port Connector; 3200 PSI Max relief setting on A port and 1500 PS Max on B port; 15ft remote pendant for long-distance control.</p>\n<p>【QUICK LIFTING &amp; LOWERING】- The hydraulic dump kits are built to start quickly and reliably. The positive and negative ports need to connect with the battery correctly to delivers quick oil output. With double actions to lifting-up and lowering-down, it tackles massive works with high efficiency.</p>\n<p>【15FT CONTROLLER EASY TO USE】- This dump trailer hydraulic pump is equipped with a 6/10/12qt metal tank, solid enough to use in different hydraulic sites, mounted both in vertical/ horizontal. We offer two additional SAE#6 connectors for your replacement. The 15ft up-down control pendant can be used for a long distance.</p>\n<p>【WIDE RANGE APPLICATION】- These reliable hydraulic powerlifting kits are used in applications where extending a hydraulic cylinder is needed. It suits truck tailgate lift, scissor lift, dump trailer, lifts truck, snowplow, aerial platform, road signs, material handling, wheelchair lifts, etc.</p>\n<p>POWER PACK Maintenance:</p>\n<p>We must keep the actuators, and pipeline cleaning, to prevent dirt from entering the system.</p>\n<p>Wemust keep the tank oil level, after a work cycle, proper fill oil. Such pump suction air will cause damage to the pump and damage to the seal.</p>\n<p>100hours after the running of hydraulic oil for the first time to join, change the new oil. After using a year, about 1500 hours, then need to replace the oil.</p>\n<p>If the working environment temperature high, use hydraulic oil of high viscosity, low working environment with low viscosity hydraulic oil.</p>\n<p>POWER PACK Key Features</p>\n<p>Double Acting Hydraulic Pump</p>\n<p>POWER PACK --The electric hydraulic pump is a double-acting hydraulic pump, with strong power for lifting-up and lowering-down. Pumps are designed for long-lasting use, and reservoirs will not crack or leak even under harsh conditions.</p>\n<p>POWER PACK Compact Structure</p>\n<p>The compact hydraulic power unit is consists of an electric motor, electromagnetic coil A/B ports with 3200 PSI Max relief setting on A port, and 1500 PS Max on B port, solenoid valves, 15ft control pendant, and a 6/10/12qt reservoir.</p>\n<p>Quick Start &amp; Oil Output of POWER PACK</p>\n<p>Connected to the 12V DC motor, our dump trailer hydraulic pump has 3.0KW max power, 2.0 GPM flow, 1.1 cc/r, and with duty lasting for 3 minutes for each start, featuring quick oil output and rapid starts each time.</p>\n<p>Versatile &amp; Convenient</p>\n<p>The 12V hydraulic pump comes with a 6/10/12qt metal cylinder tank, a pressure gauge, and 2 additional connectors for replacement. Its pendant control has 15ft (4.5 m) long and is designed with up-down buttons for easy use.</p>\n<p>Vertical/ Horizontal Mount</p>\n<p>The car-lift hydraulic power unit is designed for both horizontal and vertical mounts. It manifests impressive lifting and lowering capability. It can handle hydraulic work like lifting, pressuring, bending, straightening, tilting, and cutting.</p>\n<p>POWER PACK Wide Application</p>\n<p>This power unit is widely used in stackers, small, and medium-sized lifting platforms. It is compatible with many dump trailers and movers and is a direct replacement for 12V DC remotely controlled hydraulic systems.</p>\n<p>6 Quart Double Acting Hydraulic Power Units with Hydraulic Gauge</p>\n<p>POWER PACK has unique features among the other hydraulic power unit on the market, has a powerful double-acting hydraulic cylinder pump, advanced brass pressure pump, and remote control, working excellent in lifting and pushing devices like dump trailer, lift gates, and tow trucks.</p>\n<p>Upgrade Hydraulic Power Unit</p>\n<p>Double Acting &amp; Fast Start</p>\n<p>Quick Lifting &amp; Lowering</p>\n<p>15ft Controller Easy to Use</p>\n<p>POWER PACK Specifications</p>\n<p>Mode: Double-Acting Power-Up/ Power-Down</p>\n<p>Tank Material: Metal</p>\n<p>Tank Capacity: 6L/ 6 qt/ 1.5 Gal</p>\n<p>Flow: 2.0 GPM</p>\n<p>Max. Relief Valve Setting A Port: 3200 PSI</p>\n<p>Max. Relief Valve Setting B Port: 1500 PSI</p>\n<p>Rated Speed: 2850R/MIN</p>\n<p>Voltage: DC12V</p>\n<p>Power: 1.6KW (Rated), 3.0KW (Max)</p>\n<p>Duty: 3 Min</p>\n<p>Traffic: 1.1 cc/r</p>\n<p>Rotation: Clockwise</p>\n<p>Connector: SAE # 6</p>\n<p>Mount Position: Horizontal/ Vertical</p>\n<p>Control: Solenoid and Handheld Pendant</p>\n<p>Pendant Control Length: 15ft/ 4.5 m</p>\n<p>Package Content</p>\n<p>1 x 6 Quart Double Acting Hydraulic Pump w/ Gauge</p>\n<p>1 x English Manual</p>\n<p>2 x SAE # 6 Connectors</p>\n<p>10 Quart Double Acting Hydraulic Power Unit with Hydraulic Gauge</p>\n<p>Excellent Oil Output</p>\n<p>Fully Equipment</p>\n<p>Quart: 10 Quart</p>\n<p>Reservoir: Metal Reservoir</p>\n<p>Motor voltage: DC12V</p>\n<p>Acting: Double-acting</p>\n<p>Interface: sae6</p>\n<p>Horizontal mount</p>\n<p>1500 PS Max Relief Setting on B port</p>\n<p>3200 PSI Max. Relief Setting for Increased Lifting Power on A port</p>\n<p>Hand held pendant with 15 feet(4.5m)removal cord</p>\n<p>1 x 12V DC 10 Quart double-acting power unit (with a pressure gauge)</p>\n<p>1 x Remote controlled pendant</p>\n<p>1 x set of sae6 interface</p>\n<p>1 set of seal ring &amp; gasket</p>\n<p>12 Quart Double Acting Hydraulic Power Unit with Hydraulic Gauge</p>\n<p>POWER PACK has unique features among the other hydraulic power unit on the market, has a powerful double acting hydraulic cylinder pump, advanced brass pressure pump, and remote control, working excellent in lifting and pushing devices like dump trailer, lift gates, and tow trucks.</p>\n<p>Quart: 12 Quart</p>\n<p>Connector: SAE6 (9/16\")</p>\n<p>POWER PACK Package Content</p>\n<p>1 x 12V DC 12 Quart double-acting power unit (with a pressure gauge)</p>\n<p>Reservoir Capacity</p>\n<p>15 Quart</p>\n<p>Pump Action</p>\n<p>Material of tank</p>\n<p>Pressure</p>\n<p>Rotating Speed</p>\n<p>Max.Relief Setting</p>\n<p>3200PSI</p>\n<p>1.1cc/r</p>\n<p>Welding Robot Sold by Manufacturers for petrochemical machinery</p>\n<p>Gantry robot welding GR40 for engineering machinery</p>\n\n<div class=\"article-images\">\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-007.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-008.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-009.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-010.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-011.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-012.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-013.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-014.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-015.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-016.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-017.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-018.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-018.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n</div>",
