    body: "<p>Beveling machine groove &amp; Pipe groove processing PBM4 is suitable for such making , pipeline installation unit's use of pipe fittings in the trade as the hydropower station , petroleum , chemical industry , shipbuilding ,etc.; It is pipe fittings making and pipeline that is it weld head tube end slope key equipment that bevelling processed to construct.</p>\n<p>This grade of bed can compound different jigs , Beveling machine groove can process φ 400 - straight tubes and φ 400 - the curved and first class tube end slope bevelling of φ 820 to φ1020 ; On cutter fix one angle tool holder can process the middle higher press pipe which thick to greater than 14 mm. floating tool holder can bevel the pipe which thickness is less 16mm and has 5mm out of shape, Angle knife rest regulate after the position cutting processing according to different pipe diameter by differential organization transmission; Clamping the device adopts the structure of the platform and flexibility to clamp and can expand the range of processing and reduce the pipe fittings out of shape ; Pipe fittings is it adopt power head about move and jig platform electronic method to go up and down up and down by hand to let; Electric to adopt at operating case is it operate lathe every movement to concentrate onning, convenient and reliable. Beveling machine groove --Lathe this make up by power head , tool holder , machine tool body, clamping device , electric control system ,etc. five major parts ,</p>\n<p>Beveling machine groove inclding: （1）MILLING head: This milling head is output by motor six shelf main shaft move rapidly and 3 kinds of differential knife rests is it work up rapidly to give closely to change speed through gear wheel; Tail furnished with knife rest is it advance and retreat organization to lock soon while being electronic also, can alone or with differential to is it give meanwhile using to enter. （2）cutter tool holder Can install the angle knife rest on this knife of plates , should need to regulate the corresponding position of knife rest according to processing the size of pipe diameter , can carry on the work of cutting ; The angle knife rest is moved the transmission to cut differentially rapidly. （3）machine tool body: including motorize longitudinal feed and manual traverse feed, longitudinal feed has two speed: fast , slow , two speed can with to work while being reverse alone or at the same time. （4）Clamping device /Jig platform organization: Jig seat frame install platform and hoist or lower organization while being electronic, platform have vertical , horizontal Model T trough for install pipe fittings prop up flat and flexibility clamp organization. （5）Electric control system: The electric component of Beveling machine groove is installed in the electric special-purpose case, operate the component and install in the manipulation case of the hanging type, operate on handling the case in movement of the lathe</p>\n<p>Beveling machine groove&amp; Pipe groove processing PBM4 ( beveling machine ) is used in petrochemical machinery, engineering machinery, wind power equipment, construction &amp; bridge, shipbuilding, food &amp; pharmaceutical and other industries</p>\n<p>Welding Postioner for all kind welding girth seam and Long seam</p>\n<p>Welding Positioner with 1-Axis for Robot cobot Welding</p>\n\n<div class=\"article-images\">\n<img src=\"/images/wp/PBM-1.png\" alt=\"beveling machine groove\" />\n<img src=\"/images/xbj/xbj-03.jpg\" alt=\"beveling machine groove\" />\n<img src=\"/images/wp/wp-03.jpg\" alt=\"welding girth seam\" />\n</div>",
